Package com.kpi.tuke.scql

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Filterable
    Interface used for definition of filterable classes.
    Performable
    Interface, which can perform various operations on the data structure, such as updating, deleting and dropping.
    SCQL_ISO7816
    Interface extends the ISO7816 for the SCQL ISO7816-7 constants and APDU statuses.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cursor
    Cursor class used for selecting, deleting and updating data rows inside the Performable object instances.
    Data
    The class holds the information about the rows in the database.
    DatabaseUtil  
    Filter
    The class holds information about a filter definition, such as the column name to be applied, the operand to filter, and the value to filter the column.
    ScqlApplet
    SCQL Applet class implementing the SCQL handling mechanism by definition of ISO7816-7
    ScqlDatabase
    SCQL Database is the implementation of the ISO7816-7 SCQL commands in the smart cards.
    Table
    Class table is implemented by the definition of the table in ISO 7816-7.
    View
    Class View holds the information about the view structure in databases.
